    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a reliable companion. I\u2019ve taken really good care of it, so it\u2019s still in great shape and ready for plenty more adventures! It runs smoothly and has been well-loved. If you're looking for a dependable car that\u2019s ready to hit the road today, this is the one for you. I'd love to see it go to a good home\u2014come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
